# NOUS AI — Interview Coach

> *Interviews are won in practice.*

NOUS AI is a full-stack AI-powered interview coach that adapts to your role, your level, and your goals — giving you real-time feedback, structured coaching, and a performance scorecard after every session.

Built as a demonstration of applied AI engineering: prompt engineering, LLM integration, and a production-grade React frontend backed by a FastAPI service.

---

## Live Demo

🔗 **[nous-ai.vercel.app](https://nous-ai.vercel.app)** — bring your own OpenAI API key

---

## What it does

- **5 coaching techniques** — Zero-Shot, Few-Shot, Chain-of-Thought, Role-Based, and Structured output. Each produces a meaningfully different interview experience.
- **4 interview modes** — Technical, Behavioral, Case Study, and System Design
- **3 difficulty levels** — Junior, Mid-level, Senior
- **Inline feedback** — every AI response is tagged with strength indicators and improvement notes in real time
- **Performance scorecard** — a competency breakdown (Technical Depth, Communication Clarity, Problem-Solving, System Thinking, Trade-off Reasoning) generated by the model after each session
- **Session export** — download your full transcript as a `.txt` file
- **Live cost tracking** — token usage and estimated API cost shown in the sidebar as you go

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 18, Vite, Lucide Icons |
| Backend | FastAPI, Uvicorn |
| AI | OpenAI API (GPT-4o / GPT-4o-mini) |
| Styling | Pure CSS with CSS custom properties |
| Deploy | Vercel (frontend) · Railway (backend) |

No UI component library. No CSS framework. Every style is hand-written — intentionally, to demonstrate control over design systems.

