---

## Origin

This started as a Streamlit prototype built to explore how different prompting strategies affect LLM output quality in a conversational context. The Streamlit version (`app.py`) is preserved in the repo as a reference.

The React + FastAPI rewrite came out of wanting to build something genuinely presentable — not just functional, but designed.

